    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a way to avoid IP fragmentation of large Internet Key Exchange Protocol version 2 (IKEv2) messages.  This allows IKEv2 messages to traverse network devices that do not allow IP fragments to pass through.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
